# ApplyMate environment template
# Copy to `.env` and fill in your keys. `.env` is git-ignored.
# Values starting with `your-` trigger mock/offline mode — safe for testing.

# ── Supabase (required for cloud save, auth, and Edge Functions) ─────────────
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# ── AI Provider Keys (Flutter app direct mode) ───────────────────────────────
# The app tries these in order: Supabase Edge → Claude → DeepSeek → Groq → Mock
# For production, keep keys OUT of the mobile app — set them as Supabase secrets.
# For dev/testing without Supabase, set at least ONE of the keys below.

# Claude (Anthropic) — best quality, vision support for resume scanning
# Free tier: https://console.anthropic.com  →  Get API key
# Model: claude-haiku-4-5 (fast + cheap)
CLAUDE_API_KEY=your-claude-api-key

# DeepSeek